Package xyz.fsgek.common.net.tcp

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GekTcpChannel
    This class represents a TCP/IP connection channel between local and remote endpoint.
    GekTcpChannelHandler<M>
    TCP/IP network channel callback handler.
    GekTcpClient
    TCP/IP client interface, client endpoint of GekTcpEndpoint.
    GekTcpClientHandler
    TCP/IP network handler for client actions.
    GekTcpEndpoint
    This interface represent an endpoint on the TCP/IP network: server or client.
    GekTcpServer
    TCP/IP server interface, server endpoint of GekTcpEndpoint.
    GekTcpServerHandler
    TCP/IP network handler in server endpoint.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GekTcpClient.Builder
    Builder for GekTcpClient, based on Socket.
    GekTcpServer.Builder
    Builder for GekTcpServer, based on ServerSocket.
